org.ehcache.core.spi.store

Interface Store.ValueHolder<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.function.Supplier<V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractValueHolder
    Enclosing interface:
    Store<K,V>

    public static interface Store.ValueHolder<V>
extends java.util.function.Supplier<V>
    Holds both a value, and all the metadata associated with a mapping in a Store.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static long NO_EXPIRE
      Constant value indicating no expiration - an eternal mapping.
